00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:37,240
Kim Dam Ryeong was appointed as
the Town Head of the Heupgok-Hyeon.

14
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:40,010
December 11th of the same year,

15
00:02:40,010 --> 00:02:42,510
he died at the young age of 27.

16
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:44,440
He died?

17
00:02:47,550 --> 00:02:49,450
I beg this favor of you.

18
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,460
What are you?

19
00:02:58,460 --> 00:03:03,130
Who is the dangerous one, and who is the woman?

20
00:03:06,370 --> 00:03:08,330
Who are you?

21
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:14,570
