22
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:24,350
Not a dream... but really me?

23
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:32,990
The Legend of the Blue Sea

24
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:41,930
Joon Jae, I think the power's out.

25
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:48,340
Oh!

26
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:53,880
Why is the light like this all of a sudden?
I was so scared alone.

27
00:03:58,020 --> 00:03:59,380
You're not scared anymore, right?

28
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:02,820
Yeah, I'm fine now.

29
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:04,920
Anyway, did you get a good look?

30
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,590
Sure. Let's go.

31
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:10,560
