Don't you have to get home?

33
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:17,700
I'm fine.

34
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:22,610
Our curator said that the guy from Joseon
period looks as handsome as a K-pop singer.

35
00:04:22,610 --> 00:04:24,740
She said so.

36
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:41,730
You saw all of it, right? Let's go.

37
00:04:41,730 --> 00:04:46,570
You felt it, too, right? He looks exactly like you.

38
00:04:46,570 --> 00:04:47,530
Like me?

39
00:04:47,530 --> 00:04:49,900
Can't you tell?

40
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:51,970
Does having big eyes and being
handsome make them all look like me?

41
00:04:51,970 --> 00:04:56,070
No, he really looks like you.

42
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:59,110
Well, I can't say... I

43
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:02,550
I look better.

44
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:04,320
Let's go.

45
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:12,460
Perhaps, could he be your ancestor?

46
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:18,660
No, wait, you're a Heo.
Maybe, he's from your mother's side?

47
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:20,430
Why are you being like that?

48
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:24,770
I mean, take a look through your ancestry.

49
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:30,840
This is weird. Maybe, isn't the reason you
were really interested in Kim Dam Ryeong

50
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:33,450
because of the blood relation?

51
00:05:33,450 --> 00:05:35,850
- Cha Si Ah. - Yes?

52
00:05:35,850 --> 00:05:38,980
- The fact that we came here. - Yeah.

53
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:41,590
Let's just keep that to ourselves.

54
00:05:41,590 --> 00:05:43,160
Why?

55
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:48,590
This place is off-limits to unauthorized
personnel. I don't want to get you in trouble,

56
00:05:48,590 --> 00:05:54,170
and I'm in the middle of figuring something out.
I would like it if only you knew about this.

57
00:05:54,170 --> 00:05:57,100
Sure, I'll do that.

58
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:39,810
Why do I keep getting this dream? I don't like it.

59
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:49,550
Episode 10

60
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:54,160
What's going on, Heo Joon Jae? Why aren't you
coming back after getting Cha Si Ah's phone call?

61
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:06,540
