00:54:25,640 --> 00:54:29,750
That I... am a mermaid.

731
00:54:31,550 --> 00:54:34,220
I was looking at the painting on the vase

732
00:54:37,620 --> 00:54:40,690
and it may sound like crazy talk, but

733
00:54:40,690 --> 00:54:46,000
thoughts of that man in the
painting being me come to mind.

734
00:55:11,720 --> 00:55:14,030
Where did she go again?

735
00:55:23,600 --> 00:55:26,170
Everything repeats itself.

736
00:55:26,910 --> 00:55:31,910
My Lord, have you heard about the mermaid?

737
00:55:33,910 --> 00:55:38,950
Kim Dam Ryeong. He was a town head of Heuppgok.

738
00:55:38,950 --> 00:55:43,090
To celebrate the first day of the new town head,

739
00:55:43,090 --> 00:55:47,990
I plan on presenting a rare spectacle.

740
00:55:48,830 --> 00:55:54,370
I dream. In that dream,
I am living in a strange world.

741
00:55:54,370 --> 00:55:58,900
And also, you are there.

742
00:56:00,510 --> 00:56:02,570
Look at this. The clothes that the man is wearing.

743
00:56:02,570 --> 00:56:07,210
It seems like clothes nowadays. As if it's
a painting while looking at the future.

744
00:56:07,210 --> 00:56:13,750
And on top of that, a mermaid. Isn't it mysterious?

745
00:56:14,820 --> 00:56:22,490
♬ If we can walk as far as the blue sea's horizon ♬

746
00:56:22,530 --> 00:56:25,100
Everything repeats itself.

747
00:56:25,100 --> 00:56:29,230
The fate in this world is
continuing in that world.

748
00:56:29,230 --> 00:56:31,540
It's the same way with ill-fate.

749
00:56:32,440 --> 00:56:38,310
Protect that woman against
the dangerous person.

750
00:56:46,050 --> 00:56:49,520
A long time ago, a young lad loved a mermaid.

751
00:56:49,590 --> 00:56:52,820
He heard the mermaid's voice.

752
00:56:52,820 --> 00:56:55,590
Save me.

753
00:56:55,590 --> 00:56:57,960
I'm also different. Heo Joon Jae.

754
00:56:57,960 --> 00:56:59,930
If he realizes that I'm different

755
00:56:59,930 --> 00:57:05,200
Heo Joon Jae will hate me. He will leave.

756
00:57:05,200 --> 00:57:07,540
Don't come, Heo Joon Jae!

757
00:57:07,540 --> 00:57:11,510
But he didn't know an important thing.

758
00:57:11,510 --> 00:57:16,880
Mermaids have a special ability.

759
00:57:18,480 --> 00:57:24,060
Through a kiss, she can erase
herself in the memory of a human.

760
00:57:24,760 --> 00:57:30,830
That way, the mermaid disappeared
like foam in the young lad's memory.

761
00:57:32,300 --> 00:57:39,300
♬ If we can walk as far as the blue sea's horizon ♬

762
00:57:40,410 --> 00:57:47,080
What are you? Why are you still here?

763
00:57:47,080 --> 00:57:55,250
♬ I am afraid being under the same sky ♬

764
00:57:55,250 --> 00:58:02,930
♬ together with you will be erased. ♬

765
00:58:02,990 --> 00:58:14,070
♬ If we can walk as far as the blue sea's horizon ♬

766
00:58:14,110 --> 00:58:19,680
♬ I won't let go of your hand. ♬

767
00:58:19,680 --> 00:58:22,350
I love you.

768
00:58:38,600 --> 00:58:43,740
♬ You are someone I want
within my reach to the end ♬

769
00:58:43,740 --> 00:58:46,740
♬ Until the last moment of my life ♬

770
00:58:46,770 --> 00:58:56,010
♬ Somewhere and sometime, as I met and loved you ♬

771
00:58:56,080 --> 00:59:03,790
♬  If I see you like someone
receding in the distance ♬

772
00:59:03,820 --> 00:59:09,700
♬ Somewhere within me keeps aching ♬

773
00:59:09,700 --> 00:59:17,870
♬ Somewhere sometime we will again grow apart  ♬

774
00:59:17,870 --> 00:59:24,180
♬ I am afraid of being forgotten.  ♬

